<lb n="0170a09"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0170a10"/>
<lb n="0170a11"/><head type="no">No. 2044</head>
<lb n="0170a12"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="0170002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】奈良時代寫法然院藏本，〔天尊說〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">【原】麗本，【甲】奈良時代寫法然院藏本，〔天尊說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170002"><lem>天尊說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0170002" place="foot" type="rest">【原】麗本，【甲】奈良時代寫法然院藏本</note>阿育王譬喻經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0170a13"/>
<lb n="0170a14"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0170003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名附東晉錄〕六字－【宋】【宮】，人名＝今【元】，人名今【明】</note><note n="0170003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔人名附東晉錄〕六字－【宋】【宮】，人名＝今【元】，＝人名今【明】</note><app n="0170003"><lem>人名附東晉錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">今附東晉錄</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">人名今</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0170a15"/><div1 type="jing"><p>昔有大國王。字名阿育。統領諸國莫不臣屬。
<lb n="0170a16"/>大王聰明智慧無量。教問諸臣。天下頗有不
<lb n="0170a17"/>屬我者不。諸臣對曰。天下盡屬大王。無不
<lb n="0170a18"/><note n="0170004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弭＝糜【三】【宮】，彌【甲】</note><note n="0170004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">弭＝糜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝彌【甲】</note><app n="0170004"><lem>弭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">糜</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">彌</rdg></app>伏。中有一智臣對曰。王界內不屬王者。海
<lb n="0170a19"/>中有龍王不屬大王。初不遣信亦無貢獻。是
<lb n="0170a20"/>以知不屬大王。王可<note n="0170005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">試＝識【甲】</note><app n="0170005"><lem>試</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">識</rdg></app>之。千乘萬騎。<note n="0170006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搥＝椎【三】【宮】，推【甲】</note><note n="0170006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搥＝椎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝推【甲】</note><app n="0170006"><lem>搥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">椎</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">推</rdg></app>鍾
<lb n="0170a21"/>鳴鼓。旌旗護<note n="0170007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">憐＝擁【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">憐＝擁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170007"><lem>憐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">擁</rdg></app>前後到海邊。龍王靜然不出。
<lb n="0170a22"/>王便呼言。汝在我界內。所由不出。亦寂然不
<lb n="0170a23"/>對王。王便問智臣。何由使龍王得出。智臣對
<lb n="0170a24"/>曰。可使出耳。龍王福德甚大。以是不肯<note n="0170008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歸服＝歸伏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歸服＝歸伏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170008"><lem>歸
<lb n="0170a25"/>服</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">歸伏</rdg></app>。大王若不信臣語者。等<note n="0170009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">稱＝秤【三】</note><note n="0170009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稱＝秤【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0170009"><lem>稱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">秤</rdg></app>二斤金鑄作二
<lb n="0170a26"/>像。一作王像。一作龍王像。復取<note n="0170010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">秤＝稱【甲】＊</note><app n="0170010"><lem>秤</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">稱</rdg></app>之。龍王
<lb n="0170a27"/>像重。大王像輕。是以知龍王福德多。大王福
<lb n="0170a28"/>德少。王心甚解。歡喜無量。<note n="0170011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（普）＋告【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（普）＋告【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170011"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">普告</rdg></app>天下侍養孤
<lb n="0170a29"/>老。周窮濟<note n="0170012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乏＝之【甲】</note><app n="0170012"><lem>乏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>。所在郡縣興立天尊祠。及置
<pb ed="T" id="T50.2044.0170b" n="0170b"/>
<lb n="0170b01"/>天尊舍<note n="0170013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＋（弗）【甲】</note><app n="0170013"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">利弗</rdg></app>供養<note n="0170014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾＋（僧）【三】，〔眾〕－【宮】</note><note n="0170014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾＋（僧）【宋】【元】【明】，〔眾〕－【宮】</note><app n="0170014"><lem>眾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">眾僧</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。三年之中復取龍像王
<lb n="0170b02"/>像<app type="＊" source="0170010"><lem>秤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">稱</rdg></app>之。龍像便輕。王像便重。智臣白王。龍
<lb n="0170b03"/>可伏矣。便設鹵<note n="0170015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">簿＝蓐【甲】</note><app n="0170015"><lem>簿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">蓐</rdg></app>如前後復到海邊。龍王化
<lb n="0170b04"/>作年少婆羅門。於王前長跪問訊起居。<note n="0170016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貢＝真【甲】</note><app n="0170016"><lem>貢</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app>
<lb n="0170b05"/>獻海中所有珍<note n="0170017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寶〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔寶〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170017"><lem>寶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>奇好寶。自稱臣妾。率土
<lb n="0170b06"/>之民無不歡喜。別在經<note n="0170018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">文＝久【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0170018"><lem>文</lem><rdg wit="【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">久</rdg></app>。以示後世人。天
<lb n="0170b07"/>下多力無過福德。人護經法如母護子。豈
<lb n="0170b08"/><note n="0170019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不可＝可不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不可＝可不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170019"><lem>不可</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">可不</rdg></app>思之</p>
<lb n="0170b09"/><p>昔天尊在世時。將諸弟子教化群生見地有
<lb n="0170b10"/>一紙。弟子阿難輒便取之。天尊告阿難放地。
<lb n="0170b11"/>阿難即便放地。手便大香。小復前行見飄風
<lb n="0170b12"/>吹草在地。阿難復取。天尊語阿難放地。手便
<lb n="0170b13"/>臭。阿難未解。須臾前到精舍當問此意。阿難
<lb n="0170b14"/>白<note n="0170020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世尊＝天尊【三】</note><note n="0170020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世尊＝天尊【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0170020"><lem>世尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">天尊</rdg></app>。何緣捉紙而手香。捉草令手臭。天
<lb n="0170b15"/>尊語阿難。紙本從香地來。香著紙。是以使汝
<lb n="0170b16"/>手香。草從臭地來故。是以使汝手臭。與<note n="0170021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賢＋（人）【甲】</note><app n="0170021"><lem>賢</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賢人</rdg></app>
<lb n="0170b17"/>相近如香著紙。與惡人相近如臭著草。是以
<lb n="0170b18"/>經言近賢成智。近愚益惑。損我者三。益我者
<lb n="0170b19"/>三。此之<note n="0170022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謂＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170022"><lem>謂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">謂也</rdg></app>不可不<note n="0170023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慎＝思【甲】</note><app n="0170023"><lem>慎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">思</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0170b20"/><p>昔天尊將諸弟子至江邊。天尊語弟子。取如
<lb n="0170b21"/>拳許石。擲著水中為浮為沒。弟子對曰。石
<lb n="0170b22"/>沒在水底。天尊言。無有緣故。復次有一石
<lb n="0170b23"/><note n="0170024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辟＝壁【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0170024"><lem>辟</lem><rdg wit="【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">壁</rdg></app>方三尺。著於水上經便<note n="0170025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渡＝度【三】【宮】【甲】下同</note><note n="0170025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">渡＝度【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】下同</note><app n="0170025"><lem>渡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">度</rdg></app>河石亦不濕
<lb n="0170b24"/>云何得爾。諸弟子未解僉然怪之。諸弟子長
<lb n="0170b25"/>跪白佛言。何緣如<note n="0170026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝是【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0170026"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【甲】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>。天尊言。有善緣故耳。
<lb n="0170b26"/>何者為緣船。是天尊借為喻。與善師相值者。
<lb n="0170b27"/>得<note n="0170027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">免＝勉【甲】</note><app n="0170027"><lem>免</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">勉</rdg></app>眾苦。與惡師相值者。則習惡事不離
<lb n="0170b28"/>眾禍。示語後世之人。不可不慎</p>
<lb n="0170b29"/><p>昔有窮寒孤獨老公。無以自業。<note n="0170028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇＝偶【甲】</note><app n="0170028"><lem>遇</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">偶</rdg></app>市得一
<pb ed="T" id="T50.2044.0170c" n="0170c"/>
<lb n="0170c01"/><note n="0170029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斧＝斫【甲】＊</note><app n="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">斫</rdg></app>。是眾寶之英。而不識之。持行斫杖賣之。
<lb n="0170c02"/>以供微命用<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>欲盡。見外國治生大<note n="0170030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賈＝估【甲】</note><app n="0170030"><lem>賈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">估</rdg></app>客。
<lb n="0170c03"/>名曰薩薄。見<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>識之。便問老公。賣此<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>不。
<lb n="0170c04"/>老公言。我仰此<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>斫杖生活不賣也。薩薄復
<lb n="0170c05"/>言。與公絹百匹何以不賣。公謂調己。亦不應
<lb n="0170c06"/>和。薩薄復言。何以不見應和。與公二百匹。公
<lb n="0170c07"/>便<note n="0170031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悵＝長跪【甲】</note><app n="0170031"><lem>悵</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">長跪</rdg></app>然不樂。薩薄復言。嫌少當益。公何以
<lb n="0170c08"/>不樂。與公五百匹。公便大啼哭言。我不恨絹
<lb n="0170c09"/>少。我愚癡此<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>長尺半斫地已盡。餘有五
<lb n="0170c10"/>寸猶得五百匹。是以為恨耳。薩薄復言。勿
<lb n="0170c11"/>復遺恨。今與公千匹。即便破券持去。此<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>
<lb n="0170c12"/>眾寶之英耳。<note n="0170032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＝地【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0170032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩＝地【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0170032"><lem>薩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">地</rdg></app>博不問多少以<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>著上。薪
<lb n="0170c13"/>火燒之盡成貴寶。天尊借以為喻。<note n="0170033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【宮】</note><app n="0170033"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>受人身
<lb n="0170c14"/>六情完具聰智辯達。當就明師以求<note n="0170034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">度＝展【三】</note><note n="0170034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">度＝展【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0170034"><lem>度</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">展</rdg></app>世之
<lb n="0170c15"/>道。神通可及。而俗著不別真偽者。耕犁因放
<lb n="0170c16"/>時世取驅。至於老死復當受罪。喻如老公用
<lb n="0170c17"/>寶<app type="＊" source="0170029"><lem>斧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斫</rdg></app>盡。豈不<note n="0170035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誤＝悟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誤＝悟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170035"><lem>誤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悟</rdg></app>哉。昔隴上一鳥字為鸚鵡。
<lb n="0170c18"/>展轉及得在東太山。諸禽<note n="0170036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔獸〕－【甲】</note><app n="0170036"><lem>獸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>飛鳥莫不敬愛。
<lb n="0170c19"/>以其在遠來故。比作親友甚相愛樂。春月
<lb n="0170c20"/>野火所燒便行入水。飛在火上<note n="0170037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">抖擻＝水凍【甲】</note><app n="0170037"><lem>抖擻</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">水凍</rdg></app>毛羽之
<lb n="0170c21"/>水。救親友難。往返非一。悲鳴大<note n="0170038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吁＝呼【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0170038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吁＝呼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0170038"><lem>吁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">呼</rdg></app>鸚鵡之
<lb n="0170c22"/>水豈能滅火。至<note n="0170039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誠＝成【甲】</note><app n="0170039"><lem>誠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>感天為之降雨。火即時
<lb n="0170c23"/>得滅。天尊經借以為喻。賢者以道士遠到研
<lb n="0170c24"/>精行道。減割身口侵妻子分供養眾僧。雖無
<lb n="0170c25"/>神通感動。亦以至誠燒香求<note n="0170040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅挾＝滅使【宋】，啟使【元】【明】【甲】，滅殃【宮】</note><note n="0170040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滅挾＝滅使【宋】，＝啟使【元】【明】【甲】，＝滅殃【宮】</note><app n="0170040"><lem>滅。挾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">滅使</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">啟使</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">滅殃</rdg></app><note n="0170041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝護【宮】</note><app n="0170041"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">護</rdg></app><note n="0170042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮起＝檀越【三】【甲】</note><note n="0170042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮起＝檀越【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0170042"><lem>禮
<lb n="0170c26"/>起</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">檀越</rdg></app>獲福無量。喻如天雨眾<note n="0170043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">災＝火【三】【宮】</note><note n="0170043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">災＝火【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0170043"><lem>災</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">火</rdg></app>悉滅</p>
<lb n="0170c27"/><p>昔有大長者財富無<note n="0170044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">量＝數【甲】</note><app n="0170044"><lem>量</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">數</rdg></app>。窖穀千斛後出之不
<lb n="0170c28"/>見穀。見一小兒可年三歲亦不知語。長者
<lb n="0170c29"/>亦不知字名何物。舉門前大道邊。陌上行人
<pb ed="T" id="T50.2044.0171a" n="0171a"/>
<lb n="0171a01"/><note n="0171001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尚＝儻【元】【明】，償【甲】</note><note n="0171001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尚＝儻【元】【明】，＝償【甲】</note><app n="0171001"><lem>尚</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">儻</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">償</rdg></app>有識者。<note n="0171002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">舍＝會【甲】</note><app n="0171002"><lem>舍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">會</rdg></app>東有一車來。乘駕黃牛人著
<lb n="0171a02"/>黃衣從人皆黃。過見小兒便言。穀賊何以坐
<lb n="0171a03"/>此。是兒五穀之神。語長者持鍬。斧來。我語
<lb n="0171a04"/>君一<note n="0171003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盆＝貪【甲】</note><app n="0171003"><lem>盆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">貪</rdg></app>金處。適始行過者是金神。順陌<note n="0171004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西＝面【三】，而【宮】，惡【甲】</note><note n="0171004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西＝面【宋】【元】【明】，＝而【宮】，＝惡【甲】</note><app n="0171004"><lem>西</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">面</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">而</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惡</rdg></app>
<lb n="0171a05"/>去得道南迴。行二百步。道西當有朽故樹。其
<lb n="0171a06"/>下有<note n="0171005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00140;＝瓮【宮】＊</note><app n="0171005"><lem>&CB00140;</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">瓮</rdg></app>有十斛金。君往掘取可以還君穀直。
<lb n="0171a07"/>長者即<note n="0171006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔隨〕－【甲】</note><app n="0171006"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>小兒教得此治家足成大富。佛經
<lb n="0171a08"/>借以為喻。供養眾僧廣設檀會交有所費。喻
<lb n="0171a09"/>以失穀。道士講<note n="0171007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝教【甲】</note><app n="0171007"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">教</rdg></app>說<note n="0171008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔義〕－【甲】</note><app n="0171008"><lem>義</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>教人遠惡就<note n="0171009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔善後…無〕五字－【甲】</note><app n="0171009" word-count="5"><lem>善。
<lb n="0171a10"/>後獲福無</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>量乃可至道。喻如得金<app type="＊" source="0171005"><lem>&CB00140;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">瓮</rdg></app>。示語
<lb n="0171a11"/>後世人。福德不可不作。後悔無及</p>
<lb n="0171a12"/><p>昔有國豐盛安樂無所渴乏。便語<note n="0171010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝火【甲】</note><app n="0171010"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">火</rdg></app>臣。遣一
<lb n="0171a13"/>可使之臣。至於他國市吾所無者市來。即遣
<lb n="0171a14"/>一人往至他國益<note n="0171011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">將＝持【甲】</note><app n="0171011"><lem>將</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">持</rdg></app>珍寶遍市肆觀<note n="0171012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">看＝者【甲】</note><app n="0171012"><lem>看</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>無有
<lb n="0171a15"/><note n="0171013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餘＝俞【甲】</note><app n="0171013"><lem>餘</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">俞</rdg></app>物。盡是我國中所有耳。<note n="0171014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">最＝窮【甲】</note><app n="0171014"><lem>最</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">窮</rdg></app>後見一賢者
<lb n="0171a16"/>空坐肆上。便問之言。不見君有所賣。何以空
<lb n="0171a17"/>坐。答言在此賣智慧耳。問曰。君<note n="0171015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＋（慧）【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0171015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＋（慧）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0171015"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">智慧</rdg></app>何像賣
<lb n="0171a18"/>索幾許。答言。吾智慧直五百兩金。前稱爾金
<lb n="0171a19"/>吾當與汝說之耳。遠人便自念。我國中無賣
<lb n="0171a20"/>智慧與人。便<app type="＊" source="0170010"><lem>秤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">稱</rdg></app>五百兩金與其人。即與說
<lb n="0171a21"/>智慧之言。<note n="0171016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二十＋（一）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0171016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二十＋（一）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0171016"><lem>二十</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">二十一</rdg></app>字言。長慮諦思惟。不當
<lb n="0171a22"/><note n="0171017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">卒＝年【甲】</note><app n="0171017"><lem>卒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">年</rdg></app>行怒。今日雖不用。會當有用時。於是受
<lb n="0171a23"/><note n="0171018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝訟【甲】</note><app n="0171018"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訟</rdg></app>令利各自還家。臣買得智慧之言即便還
<lb n="0171a24"/>國道徑其家。夜入<note n="0171019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明月＝月明見【三】【宮】</note><note n="0171019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明月＝月明見【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0171019"><lem>明月</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">月明見</rdg></app>婦床前有兩<note n="0171020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（色）＋履【三】【宮】</note><note n="0171020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（色）＋履【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0171020"><lem>履</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">色履</rdg></app>。疑
<lb n="0171a25"/>有異人便生惡念。其婦卒得疾病母往宿。視
<lb n="0171a26"/>長者故說智慧之言未休。其母驚覺兒<note n="0171021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾〕－【甲】</note><app n="0171021"><lem>爾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>來
<lb n="0171a27"/>歸<note n="0171022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝那【甲】</note><app n="0171022"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">那</rdg></app>。兒<note n="0171023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使【甲】</note><app n="0171023"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>走出戶呼賤賤。母問其言。云何
<lb n="0171a28"/>汝行為得何物。何以呼賤。兒言我母以婦萬
<lb n="0171a29"/>兩金猶不與人。正顧五百兩金豈非賤<note n="0171024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【甲】</note><app n="0171024"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">邪</rdg></app>。
<pb ed="T" id="T50.2044.0171b" n="0171b"/>
<lb n="0171b01"/>天尊經借以為喻。諺語一言之助。勝千金之
<lb n="0171b02"/>益。此之謂也</p>
<lb n="0171b03"/><p>昔天尊在<note n="0171025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洹＝&M010527;【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0171025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洹＝&M010527;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0171025"><lem>洹</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&M010527;</rdg></app>水邊。廣說經法。時天龍鬼神帝
<lb n="0171b04"/>王<note n="0171026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝之【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0171026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人＝之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0171026"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>民飛鳥走<note n="0171027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獸＝狩【宋】【元】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0171027"><lem>獸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">狩</rdg></app>皆來聽法。時有放牛老
<lb n="0171b05"/>公柱杖而聽。不覺杖下有蝦蟆。蝦蟆聽經意
<lb n="0171b06"/>美。亦不覺背上有杖。遂久蝦蟆命終。其神即
<lb n="0171b07"/>生天上。用天眼觀其本。從何道中來乃見故
<lb n="0171b08"/>身在蝦蟆中。來天華散其故身上。示語後世
<lb n="0171b09"/>人。蝦蟆中聽經意美得生天上。況<note n="0171028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝杖【宮】，枚【甲】</note><note n="0171028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於＝杖【宮】，＝枚【甲】</note><app n="0171028"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">杖</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">枚</rdg></app>賢者至
<lb n="0171b10"/>心聽經。豈不巍巍乎</p>
<lb n="0171b11"/><p>昔有兄弟二人。弟行追明師作沙門。遂得羅
<lb n="0171b12"/>漢道。數數來語兄。可勤作福德。兄言。我<note n="0171029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＋（心念）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0171029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">今＋（心念）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0171029"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">今心念</rdg></app>
<lb n="0171b13"/><note n="0171030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00229;＝忽【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0171030"><lem>&CB00229;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">忽</rdg></app>務且須後耳。數數非一。兄後命終。弟以
<lb n="0171b14"/>道眼觀兄神生何道。看天道人道<note n="0171031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【甲】</note><app n="0171031"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中不見
<lb n="0171b15"/>其神。復觀地獄餓鬼道中復不見。乃在畜生
<lb n="0171b16"/>道中。見兄神作大牛。時賈客駕牛治生。道惡
<lb n="0171b17"/>趺泥中不能自起。賈客以杖打之。猶復舒咽
<lb n="0171b18"/>不起。弟見兄如此。逕來在牛前。語兄言。今日
<lb n="0171b19"/><app type="＊" source="0171030"><lem>&CB00229;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">忽</rdg></app>務何如本時。牛便<note n="0171032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羞＝著【元】【明】</note><app n="0171032"><lem>羞</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>慚感絕而死。道人
<lb n="0171b20"/>即去。眾<note n="0171033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賈＝寶【甲】</note><app n="0171033"><lem>賈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寶</rdg></app>人等便共議言。道人何故來<note n="0171034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＝祝【甲】</note><app n="0171034"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">祝</rdg></app>
<lb n="0171b21"/>殺我牛。便追逐道人。將還問其意狀。道人如
<lb n="0171b22"/>事為說牛是我兄。不隨我語以致此罪。道人
<lb n="0171b23"/>便擲&CB00425;虛空。飛隨其後。眾賈人知是聖人。乃
<lb n="0171b24"/>更自責。為牛燒香作福。其福得生天上</p>
<lb n="0171b25"/><p>昔有賢者。居舍衛國<note n="0171035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">東南＝南東【甲】</note><app n="0171035"><lem>東南</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">南東</rdg></app>三十里。家門奉法
<lb n="0171b26"/>供養道人。家公好喜殺&CB00337;賣肉。道人漸漸知
<lb n="0171b27"/>之。未及呵誡。老公遂便命終。在&M010527;水中受鬼
<lb n="0171b28"/>神形。有<note n="0171036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝白【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0171036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自＝白【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0171036"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">白</rdg></app>鐵輪鋒刃如霜雪。隨流刺之。苦
<lb n="0171b29"/>痛不可言。後日道人渡&M010527;水在正與鬼神相
<pb ed="T" id="T50.2044.0171c" n="0171c"/>
<lb n="0171c01"/>值。其鬼便出半身在水上。<note n="0171037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捉＝投【甲】</note><app n="0171037"><lem>捉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">投</rdg></app>船顧言。捉道
<lb n="0171c02"/>人著水中。不者盡殺船上人。時有一賢者便
<lb n="0171c03"/>問鬼神。何以故索是道人。鬼神言。我在世間
<lb n="0171c04"/><note n="0171038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【宮】，時＝門【甲】</note><app n="0171038"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門</rdg></app>供養道人。道人心知我殺&CB00337;賣肉。而不呵
<lb n="0171c05"/>誡我。是以殺道人耳。賢者便言。君坐殺&CB00337;乃
<lb n="0171c06"/>致此罪。今復欲殺道人。罪豈不多乎。鬼神思
<lb n="0171c07"/>惟實如賢者之言。便放令去。道人得去還語
<lb n="0171c08"/>其家子孫。為作追福。神即<note n="0171039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝德【甲】</note><app n="0171039"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app>免苦。示語後
<lb n="0171c09"/>世人。道人受供養不可不教誡</p>
<lb n="0171c10"/><p>昔有人在道上行。見道有一死人。鬼神以杖
<lb n="0171c11"/>鞭之。行人問言。此人<note n="0171040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【甲】</note><app n="0171040"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>死何故鞭之。鬼神
<lb n="0171c12"/>言。是我故身。<note n="0171041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在生＝生在【甲】</note><app n="0171041"><lem>在生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生在</rdg></app>之日不孝父母。事君不
<lb n="0171c13"/>忠。不敬三尊。不隨師父之教。令我墮罪苦
<lb n="0171c14"/>痛<note n="0171042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">難＝勤【甲】</note><app n="0171042"><lem>難</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">勤</rdg></app>言。悉我故身故來鞭耳。稍稍前行復見
<lb n="0171c15"/>一死人。天神來下散華於死人屍上。以手摩
<lb n="0171c16"/><note n="0171043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01288;＝抄【宮】，挲【甲】＊</note><note n="0171043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01288;＝抄【宮】，＝挲【甲】＊</note><app n="0171043"><lem>&CB01288;</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">抄</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">挲</rdg></app>之。行人問言。觀君似是天。何故摩<app type="＊" source="0171043"><lem>&CB01288;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">挲</rdg></app>是
<lb n="0171c17"/>死屍。答曰。是我故身生時之日孝順父母。忠
<lb n="0171c18"/>信事君。奉敬三尊。承受師父之教。令我神得
<lb n="0171c19"/>生天。皆是故身之恩。是以來報之耳。行人一
<lb n="0171c20"/>日見<note n="0171044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此〕－【甲】</note><app n="0171044"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>二變。便還家奉持五戒修行十善。
<lb n="0171c21"/>孝順父母忠信事君。示語後世人。罪福追人
<lb n="0171c22"/>久而不置。不可不慎</p>
<lb n="0171c23"/><p>昔有道人。在山中學<note n="0171045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（道）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0171045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道＋（道）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0171045"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">道道</rdg></app>。人遣沙彌出舍
<lb n="0171c24"/><note n="0171046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（分）＋衛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0171046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（分）＋衛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0171046"><lem>衛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">分衛</rdg></app>。日日責一<note n="0171047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斗＝舛【三】【宮】【甲】＊</note><note n="0171047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斗＝舛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】＊</note><app n="0171047"><lem>斗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">舛</rdg></app>米兼課一偈。市中有一坐
<lb n="0171c25"/>肆賢者。見沙彌並語而行。問沙彌言。周行
<lb n="0171c26"/>走索何以並語而行。沙彌答言。我師在山
<lb n="0171c27"/>中學道。日責我米一<app type="＊" source="0171047"><lem>斗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】">舛</rdg></app>兼課一偈。是以並
<lb n="0171c28"/>行誦一偈耳。賢者復問。若不輸米日可<note n="0171048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諳＝菴【甲】</note><note n="0171048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諳＝菴【甲】<app><lem resp="march">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0171048"><lem>諳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">菴</rdg></app>
<lb n="0171c29"/>幾偈。言可<app type="＊" source="0171048"><lem>諳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">菴</rdg></app>十偈。賢者便言。勿復分<note n="0171049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝衛【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0171049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝衛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0171049"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">衛</rdg></app>。
<pb ed="T" id="T50.2044.0172a" n="0172a"/>
<lb n="0172a01"/>吾<note n="0172001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝日【甲】</note><app n="0172001"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">日</rdg></app>代沙彌輸米。沙彌歡喜即得靜坐學問。
<lb n="0172a02"/>賢者為沙彌輸<note n="0172002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔米〕－【甲】</note><app n="0172002"><lem>米</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>九斛<note n="0172003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔米〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0172003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔米〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0172003"><lem>米</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。然後試沙彌經
<lb n="0172a03"/>皆自通利。賢者後生世間為天尊作弟子。字
<lb n="0172a04"/>名阿難。天尊有十二部經典。聰明之福<note n="0172004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">報＋（悉能誦持智）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0172004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">報＋（悉能誦持智）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0172004"><lem>報</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">報悉能誦持智</rdg></app>不
<lb n="0172a05"/>可<note n="0172005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂＝量【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0172005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謂＝量【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0172005"><lem>謂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">量</rdg></app>問一知十。示語後世人。福德隨身如影
<lb n="0172a06"/>隨形。隨人所種各獲其福。不可不為</p>
<lb n="0172a07"/><p>昔有屠兒有千頭牛養令<note n="0172006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">肥＝服【甲】</note><app n="0172006"><lem>肥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">服</rdg></app>好。日殺一牛賣
<lb n="0172a08"/>肉。<note n="0172007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0172007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0172007"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>殺五百牛。餘有五百頭。方共跳騰諠
<lb n="0172a09"/>戲共相觝觸。天尊時入國。見牛如此愍而捨
<lb n="0172a10"/>去。語諸弟子。此牛愚癡。伴侶欲盡方共戲諠。
<lb n="0172a11"/>人亦如是。一日過去。人命轉<note n="0172008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">減＝滅【甲】</note><app n="0172008"><lem>減</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>不可不思惟
<lb n="0172a12"/>勤求度世之道</p>
<lb n="0172a13"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0172009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔天尊說〕－【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0172009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天尊說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0172009"><lem>天尊說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿育王譬喻經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>